      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Erin Dame</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:182px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/erindame/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/2/2c/ErinDame.jpg\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ErinDame.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Erin Dame <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Erin Dame</b>,<br />\nan American chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, and software and web developer affiliated with the Research Computing Center, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_New_Hampshire\">University of New Hampshire</a>, where he already received his BSc. degree in computer science in 1996. \nCombining his professional and avocational interests, he is working on his own chess engine dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=RookieMonster&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"RookieMonster (page does not exist)\">RookieMonster</a> since May 2016 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2017\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2017</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2018_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2018 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erin_Dame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016\">2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erin_Dame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61140\">perpetual check position</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 16, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Check#Perpetual\" title=\"Check\">Perpetual Check</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61193\">transposition table pseudocode</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 22, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61250\">Stockfish eval output</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 27, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Wrong_Color_Bishop_and_Rook_Pawn\" title=\"Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn\">Wrong Color Bishop and Rook Pawn</a>, <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61384\">transposition tables and three-fold repetition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 10, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61429\">broadcasting engine tournaments</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61453\">static evals from list of FENs?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 17, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61543\">Transposition tables in Cray Blitz</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 26, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a>, <a href=\"/Cray_Blitz\" title=\"Cray Blitz\">Cray Blitz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61780\">Winboard book settings</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 20, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a>, <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61988\">command line engine match?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 06, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">CLI</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62012\">CLOP: when to stop?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 07, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/CLOP\" title=\"CLOP\">CLOP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62654\">crazyhouse promotions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Crazyhouse\" title=\"Crazyhouse\">Crazyhouse</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2017\">2017</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erin_Dame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2017\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63438\">Penrose Puzzle</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 14, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Problems,_Compositions_and_Studies#Penrose\" title=\"Chess Problems, Compositions and Studies\">Penrose Puzzle</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63525\">Winboard variants online</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Games#ChessVariants\" title=\"Games\">Chess Variants</a>, <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63571\">crazyhouse tips?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Crazyhouse\" title=\"Crazyhouse\">Crazyhouse</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63990\">exact transposition table entries</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64093\">tt move vs null move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Hash_Move\" title=\"Hash Move\">Hash Move</a>, <a href=\"/Null_Move\" title=\"Null Move\">Null Move</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64110\">trading pieces and pawns based on material balance</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 28, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64115\">insufficient mating material</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Draw_Evaluation\" title=\"Draw Evaluation\">Draw Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=64767\">EGTB probe in search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 30, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Gaviota_Tablebases\" title=\"Gaviota Tablebases\">Gaviota Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65881\">how to create a labeled epd from pgn?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 02, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a>, <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">EPD</a>, <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">PGN</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66076\">Neural networks (NN) explained</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 20, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">Neural Networks</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2018_...\">2018 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Erin_Dame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2018 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=66554\">finding eval swings in pgn?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=68010\">Deep Learning the Rubik's Cube</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 17, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69929\">Top Engines without Piece-Square Tables?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Erin Dame</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 16, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span 